                    alt="img" 
                    src="/client/assets/images/blog_details_2_img.jpg"
                    )
              .col-sm-6
                div(class="blog_details_center_img")
                  img.img-fluid.w-100(
                    alt="img" 
                    src="/client/assets/images/blog_details_3_img.jpg"
                    )
            h4 Embracing a sophisticated yet minimalist aesthetic.
